Damage 34 - Delay 43<BR>
Weight: 7.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/warrior/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
</font>
Dropped in the Plane of Hate.<BR>

